text = <<ET= ARGF#binmode(from ~/.ri)------------------------------------------------------------------------------  ARGF.binmode  -> ARGF------------------------------------------------------------------------------Puts ARGF into binary mode. Once a stream is in binary mode, it cannot bereset to non-binary mode. This option has the following effects:* Newline conversion is disabled.* Encoding conversion is disabled.* Content is treated as ASCII-8BIT.ET# ruby ARGF#binmode.rb glark.txtARGF.binmodeputs ARGF.readlines